0w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcSet=\"/static/194602968ad9310c76a9e7b541fc817c/85b06/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs.png 256w,\n/static/194602968ad9310c76a9e7b541fc817c/bc282/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs.png 512w,\n/static/194602968ad9310c76a9e7b541fc817c/f1720/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs.png 1024w,\n/static/194602968ad9310c76a9e7b541fc817c/5ece7/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs.png 1200w\" src=\"/static/194602968ad9310c76a9e7b541fc817c/f1720/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs.png\" alt=\"Aerin Carreno, Erika Grimm, Jackie Delgado, NZ and Rudy Martinez at the ADDY Awards event\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/194602968ad9310c76a9e7b541fc817c/85b06/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs.png 256w,\n/static/194602968ad9310c76a9e7b541fc817c/bc282/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs.png 512w,\n/static/194602968ad9310c76a9e7b541fc817c/f1720/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs.png 1024w,\n/static/194602968ad9310c76a9e7b541fc817c/5ece7/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"/static/194602968ad9310c76a9e7b541fc817c/85b06/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs.png 256w,\n/static/194602968ad9310c76a9e7b541fc817c/bc282/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs.png 512w,\n/static/194602968ad9310c76a9e7b541fc817c/f1720/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs.png 1024w,\n/static/194602968ad9310c76a9e7b541fc817c/5ece7/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs.png 1200w\" src=\"/static/194602968ad9310c76a9e7b541fc817c/f1720/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs.png\" alt=\"Aerin Carreno, Erika Grimm, Jackie Delgado, NZ and Rudy Martinez at the ADDY Awards event\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></p>\n<p>We are so proud of The PM Group’s sister company, <strong><a href=\"http://www.3qmp.com\">Quarter Moon Productions</a></strong>. Since 2010, they have been producing work we often brag about, but it’s always special when they can be recognized on a broader level.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>This past weekend, some of Quarter Moon Productions’ staff attended the 2020 San Antonio American Advertising Federation Awards or ADDYs. Their team was awarded a Silver ADDY in Branded Broadcast Content &amp; Entertainment for Television for YOLO TX, a Silver ADDY in Animation, Special Effects or Motion Graphics for UTSA Insider, and a Bronze ADDY in Animation, Special Effects or Motion Graphics for Friday Night Blitz. Congratulations QMP! An outstanding job for the hard work your team puts in every day to create unique and engaging content.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5239 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:600px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:100%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/530382a175d7aa552a41fa3ea7258db9/650b0/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-1.png 150w,\n/static/530382a175d7aa552a41fa3ea7258db9/f2d49/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-1.png 300w,\n/static/530382a175d7aa552a41fa3ea7258db9/ff59c/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-1.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" srcSet=\"/static/530382a175d7aa552a41fa3ea7258db9/650b0/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-1.png 150w,\n/static/530382a175d7aa552a41fa3ea7258db9/f2d49/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-1.png 300w,\n/static/530382a175d7aa552a41fa3ea7258db9/ff59c/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-1.png 600w\" src=\"/static/530382a175d7aa552a41fa3ea7258db9/ff59c/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-1.png\" alt=\"Erika Grimm, Aerin Carreno and Jackie Delgado with QMP ADDY award\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/530382a175d7aa552a41fa3ea7258db9/650b0/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-1.png 150w,\n/static/530382a175d7aa552a41fa3ea7258db9/f2d49/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-1.png 300w,\n/static/530382a175d7aa552a41fa3ea7258db9/ff59c/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-1.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" srcset=\"/static/530382a175d7aa552a41fa3ea7258db9/650b0/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-1.png 150w,\n/static/530382a175d7aa552a41fa3ea7258db9/f2d49/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-1.png 300w,\n/static/530382a175d7aa552a41fa3ea7258db9/ff59c/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-1.png 600w\" src=\"/static/530382a175d7aa552a41fa3ea7258db9/ff59c/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-1.png\" alt=\"Erika Grimm, Aerin Carreno and Jackie Delgado with QMP ADDY award\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span><span class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5240 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:600px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:100%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/ead40ebc6fc4a748bdb35347cb16a9a6/650b0/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-2.png 150w,\n/static/ead40ebc6fc4a748bdb35347cb16a9a6/f2d49/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-2.png 300w,\n/static/ead40ebc6fc4a748bdb35347cb16a9a6/ff59c/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-2.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" srcSet=\"/static/ead40ebc6fc4a748bdb35347cb16a9a6/650b0/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-2.png 150w,\n/static/ead40ebc6fc4a748bdb35347cb16a9a6/f2d49/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-2.png 300w,\n/static/ead40ebc6fc4a748bdb35347cb16a9a6/ff59c/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-2.png 600w\" src=\"/static/ead40ebc6fc4a748bdb35347cb16a9a6/ff59c/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-2.png\" alt=\"NZ and Rudy Martinez with 3 QMP ADDY awards\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/ead40ebc6fc4a748bdb35347cb16a9a6/650b0/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-2.png 150w,\n/static/ead40ebc6fc4a748bdb35347cb16a9a6/f2d49/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-2.png 300w,\n/static/ead40ebc6fc4a748bdb35347cb16a9a6/ff59c/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-2.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" srcset=\"/static/ead40ebc6fc4a748bdb35347cb16a9a6/650b0/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-2.png 150w,\n/static/ead40ebc6fc4a748bdb35347cb16a9a6/f2d49/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-2.png 300w,\n/static/ead40ebc6fc4a748bdb35347cb16a9a6/ff59c/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-2.png 600w\" src=\"/static/ead40ebc6fc4a748bdb35347cb16a9a6/ff59c/Image-3.6.20-QMP-ADDYs-2.png\" alt=\"NZ and Rudy Martinez with 3 QMP ADDY awards\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div itemprop=\"video\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/VideoObject\">\n<h2><span itemprop=\"name\">Big Bend Backcountry &#8211; YOLO TX</span></h2>\n<p><meta itemprop=\"duration\" content=\"PT5M37S\" /><meta itemprop=\"uploadDate\" content=\"2019-09-03T21:46:52Z\"/><meta itemprop=\"thumbnailURL\" content=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/tOlQQZJ64sE/hqdefault.jpg\" /><meta itemprop=\"interactionCount\" content=\"670\" /><meta itemprop=\"embedURL\" content=\"https://youtube.googleapis.com/v/tOlQQZJ64sE\" /></p>\n<div id=\"schema-videoobject\" class=\"video-container\"><iframe width=\"853\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/tOlQQZJ64sE?rel=0&#038;controls=0&#038;showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><span itemprop=\"description\">Head with us to the Wild West as we explore Big Bend! The remote land of West Texas brings incredible views and one-of-a-kind experiences.</span>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com\"><strong>About The PM Group</strong></a>: The PM Group was founded in 1988. For over 31 years, the agency has continued to grow and is San Antonio’s largest advertising agency. The PM Group’s client roster spans numerous industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, non-profit, real estate and fitness. In addition, the agency hosts an annual Charity Gala that to date has raised millions of dollars for local San Antonio area non-profit organizations in the last 15 years! In the past 10 years, The PM Group has raised both directly and indirectly over $12 million for these charities. It is our way of giving back to the community that we so humbly serve.</p>\n","title":"PM Group Sister Company, Quarter Moon Productions, Takes Home Three ADDYs","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"PM Group Sister Company, Quarter Moon Productions, Takes Home Three ADDYs","url":"/sister-company-quarter-moon-productions-takes-home-three-addys/"}],"title":"Quarter Moon Productions Takes Home Three ADDYs","metaDesc":"We are proud of The PM Group’s sister company, Quarter Moon Productions. They took home three awards from the 2020 San Antonio ADDYs...","focuskw":"Quarter Moon Productions","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"Quarter Moon Productions Takes Home Three ADDYs","opengraphDescription":"We are proud of The PM Group’s sister company, Quarter Moon Productions. They took home three awards from the 2020